name: Music & Copyright Newsletter
description: Music & Copyright Newsletter is a fortnightly research service covering global copyright and legal issues affecting the music industry. Written by experts that have been involved in the music industry for 20 years, it delivers accurate analysis of music industry news and views, independently determined market share figures not available from any other source and a wide range of data and statistics. They also provide 23 country reports packed full of the latest music industry data.

meta.more_info: Click 'Newsletter Library' on the upper right corner to see the archive list of Music & Copyright Newsletter
